title: Avolon delivers Airbus A321-200 to Vueling Airlines
text:
Avolon delivers Airbus A321-200 to Vueling Airlines Adv: 
Jul 22, 2015 Adv: 
DUBLIN, Ireland - Avolon, the international aircraft leasing company, announces the delivery of an Airbus A321-200 to Vueling Airlines. Today’s delivery is Avolon’s first aircraft on lease to Vueling Airlines.
